{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "赤壁前，周瑜看着江面，心里有一个难题。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "大家已经准备了许多事情，可风向还不合适。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "诸葛亮来到江边，听见旗子轻响，又看了看云色和水面。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "他没有说神奇的话，只是安静观察。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "白天，他看云往哪里走；",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "夜里，他听江风怎样吹；",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 3,
      "text": "清晨，他又看小旗是不是转了方向。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s4.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 4,
      "text": "鲁肃问他要等多久，他说，耐心一点，东风快来了。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s5.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "诸葛亮提醒周瑜和大家，把船只、信号和人员都安排好。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "风没到时，不要抢先；",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "风一到，就按原来的计划做。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 3,
      "text": "大家听了，重新核对时间，也把容易忘的事写下来。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s4.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "到了约定的时候，江面果然吹来东风。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "小旗一面面转向，船上的人也精神起来。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "周瑜看见准备没有白费，便让大家按信号行动。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 3,
      "text": "事情顺利推进，队伍也保持了安稳。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s4.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "借东风的故事告诉我们，聪明不只是会想点子，还要会观察、会等待、会提醒朋友一起准备。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "看准时机，再一起行动，困难就会变得清楚一些。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    }
  ]
}
